nodes.title: HiDream settings
widgets_values:
## Official HiDream sampling settings

### HiDream Full

* hidream_i1_full_fp16.safetensors
* shift: 3.0
* steps: 50
* sampler: uni_pc
* scheduler: simple
* cfg: 5.0

### HiDream Dev

* hidream_i1_dev_bf16.safetensors
* shift: 6.0
* steps: 28
* sampler: lcm
* scheduler: normal
* cfg: 1.0 (no negative prompt)

### HiDream Fast

* hidream_i1_fast_bf16.safetensors
* shift: 3.0
* steps: 16
* sampler: lcm
* scheduler: normal
* cfg: 1.0 (no negative prompt)

### HiDream recommended resolutions

* 1024 x 1024
* 768 x 1360
* 1360 x 768
* 880 x 1168
* 1168 x 880
* 1248 x 832
* 832 x 1248

# HiDream E1 settings

### Steps:  28
### Resolution: 768x768

## Prompt
### Use this template, just add "instruction" and " description".
Editing Instruction: {instruction}. Target Image Description: {description}
### Example:
Editing Instruction: Convert the image into a Ghibli style. Target Image Description: A person in a light pink t-shirt with short dark hair, depicted in a Ghibli style against a plain background.
